'''''The Spanish Gypsy''''' is a 1911 American [[short film|short]] [[silent film|silent]] [[drama film]] directed by [[D. W. Griffith]], starring [[Wilfred Lucas]] and featuring [[Blanche Sweet]].<ref name="silentera">{{cite web |url=http://www.silentera.com/PSFL/data/S/SpanishGypsy1911.html |title=Silent Era: The Spanish Gypsy |accessdate=2008-07-05|work=silentera}}</ref>
